  - include a warn + make backup if dimensions change, as it won't look pretty
- support 'image' content type which loads an image from the image directory
- shuffle decks/bags when the game is loaded
- collect all parsing errors (as far as possible) and list them together
- allow dealing deck parts to new positions (such as player hand, or two draw stacks)
- allow object tracking when rebuilding (so player re-positioning is remembered, where possible) ?
- saving items to component chest?
- create a TTS image for the load file created
- allow saving as a new version instead of overwriting

- allow changing basic room settings (table model) ?

- automate documentation?
- unit tests
- actual website
  - donate button
  - download binaries
  - docs
 
